7.1  IN NO EVENT SHALL THE LICENSOR BE HELD LIABLE FOR ANY LOSS OF PROFITS, LOSS OF REVENUE, LOSS OF DATA, INTERRUPTION OF BUSINESS, OR OTHER PECUNIARY LOSS ARISING OUT OF OR RELATED TO THE USE OR INABILITY TO USE THE SOFTWARE, HOWEVER CAUSED AND ON ANY THEORY OF LIABILITY.  

