8.1  Should any provision of this License be adjudged invalid, illegal, or unenforceable under applicable law, such provision shall be severed, and the remaining provisions shall continue in full force and effect, their intent and purpose unimpaired.  
8.2  This License shall be interpreted in accordance with the grand principles of open exchange and the noble cause of unfettered collaboration.  

