X.  CONCLUSION AND FAREWELL  
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------  
Thus, in steadfast determination and with uplifted spirits, we do hereby affix our imprimatur to this America License, that it may stand as a testament to the enduring promise of freedom, fellowship, and the unbounded potential of human ingenuity.  

“May the lamp of knowledge burn ever more brightly within these United States of the Mind, and may all who traverse the vast expanses of code do so under the radiant banner of liberty.”  
